name: Guyummy Grandwarf
description: This Halloween, in the Shire, Guyummy Grandwarf has finally arrived! Right on time! One does not simply guess what's on his mind. This Grandwarf wizard uses jester magic. It is said that he lives outside of Fancoin Forest, on the east cost, in the Neverfields. Although, he's nearly impossible to find. This old little pest can deceive foes, mess with the weather and other dimensions.
